README.md
     1‚Üí# mdBook
     7‚ÜímdBook is a utility to create modern online books from Markdown files.
     8‚Üí
     9‚ÜíCheck out the **[User Guide]** for a list of features and installation and usage information.
    10‚ÜíThe User Guide also serves as a demonstration to showcase what a book looks like.
    11‚Üí
    12‚ÜíIf you are interested in contributing to the development of mdBook, check out the [Contribution Guide].
    13‚Üí
    14‚Üí## License
    16‚ÜíAll the code in this repository is released under the ***Mozilla Public License v2.0***, for more information take a look at the [LICENSE] file.
    17‚Üí
    18‚Üí[User Guide]: https://rust-lang.github.io/mdBook/
    19‚Üí[contribution guide]: https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md
    20‚Üí[LICENSE]: https://github.com/rust-lang/mdBook/blob/master/LICENSE
